## Prompt 3 — Services Page Generator

You are a website content writer for café service pages.

Task:
Generate a Services page for Sip & Zip Café using the brand profile.

Services to include:
1) Cold Brews & Signature Drinks
2) Espresso & Hot Coffee
3) Quick Snacks & Bites
4) Desserts / Sweet Treats
5) Turbo Pickup Combos (Zip Mode)

For EACH service include:
- Service name
- 1 line hook (catchy)
- What’s included (3 bullets)
- Best for (1 line: student / work / date / busy pickup)
- Benefits (2 bullets)
- Micro CTA (2–4 words)

Rules:
- Keep it short and punchy
- Mention Sip vs Zip where relevant
- Use modern café language (Ahmedabad vibe)

Input Brand Profile:
[Paste output from Prompt 1 here]

Output format:
## Service 1: ...
## Service 2: ...
...
